tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE business_performance_dashboard (
    dashboard_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    dashboard_name STRING,
    kpi_1 INT,
    kpi_2 INT,
    kpi_3 INT
);

CREATE TABLE business_data (
    entry_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    revenue FLOAT,
    cost FLOAT,
    profit FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE business_data (
    business_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    business_name VARCHAR(255),
    revenue DECIMAL,
    expenses DECIMAL,
    profit DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE KPI_Dashboard (
    KPI_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    KPI_Name VARCHAR(50),
    KPI_Description TEXT,
    KPI_Target DECIMAL,
    KPI_Current_Value DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Business_Data (
    Business_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Business_Name VARCHAR(100),
    Industry_Type VARCHAR(50),
    Revenue DECIMAL,
    Employee_Count INT
);
